This is a combined multiple recursive generator by L'Ecuyer. 
Its sequence is,
@tex
\beforedisplay
$$
z_n = (x_n - y_n) \,\hbox{mod}\, m_1
$$
\afterdisplay
@end tex
@ifinfo

@example
