@c{$m_2 = 2145483479$}
@math{m_2 = 2145483479}.

The period of this generator is  
@c{$\hbox{lcm}(m_1^3-1, m_2^3-1)$}
@math{lcm(m_1^3-1, m_2^3-1)},
